# Email (SMTP) - for notification emails
# Gmail example: SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com, SMTP_PORT=587, SMTP_USER=<your@gmail.com>, SMTP_PASS=<16-char App Password>
# Brevo example: SMTP_HOST=smtp-relay.brevo.com, SMTP_PORT=587
# If these are empty, email sending will be silently skipped.
